    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional find: a vehicle in pristine, showroom condition that defies its age. Meticulously maintained and showing zero signs of wear, this example represents the pinnacle of automotive care. From the flawless exterior finish to the untouched interior, it offers a driving experience indistinguishable from new. This is an uncompromising choice for the discerning buyer who demands nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
