      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a concours-level example of the E46 platform, optimized for the discerning driver. This chassis features a bulletproof S54 inline-six, showing exceptional compression across all cylinders with a recent VANOS overhaul using Beisan components to ensure optimal variable valve timing. The rear subframe has been proactively reinforced with bespoke plates to mitigate the known structural fatigue points of this generation. The 6-speed Getrag box provides crisp, tactile engagement via a weight-matched short-throw kit, while the limited-slip differential provides surgical power delivery through the corners. Suspension geometry is dialed in with adjustable coilovers, ensuring neutral turn-in and high-speed stability. This isn't just a car; it's a precision-engineered instrument maintained with an open-checkbook policy. Fluids have been flushed religiously with Liqui Moly synthetics. Truly a turn-key collector's piece for the purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
